    Primary: '#F25338',

    Border: '#ECECEE',
    BgLight: '#F5F5F5',
    BgDisabled: '#FAFAFA',

    TextSuccess: '#5CC688',
    TextPrimary: '#333333',
    TextInactive: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)',
    TextDisabled: '#BEBEBE',
    TextSecondary: 'rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.6)',
    TextPlaceholder: 'rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.4)',

    Gradient: ['rgb(242, 83, 56)', 'rgb(250, 131, 15)']
}

export default Colors
